  {
    "hotel_id": "484809",
    "hotel_url": "https://www.agoda.com/grand-whiz-hotel-nusa-dua/hotel/bali-id.html",
    "name": "Grand Whiz Hotel Nusa Dua",
    "detail": "This is one of many hotels in Bali that I can say... YES...!! THIS IS IT...!! Located in the luxurious area of Nusa Dua Beach complex, side by side with other higher start rating and branded hotels but Grand Whiz is cheap for this area. I booked a Superior Room, the size is so nice, just perfect... bathroom and shower is very nice and clean. Although Grand Whiz does not own its own beach space, but all guests have access to that sweet and beautiful Nusa Dua Beach... I enjoyed my afternoon and morning run in the area. Breakfast is so so... as a four star I wish they could offer more varieties, but no complain on this for me... I enjoyed it quite well. This hotel will be my first choice everytime I go to Bali now....!!",
