  {
    "hotel_id": "65512",
    "hotel_url": "https://www.agoda.com/grand-istana-rama-hotel/hotel/bali-id.html",
    "name": "Grand Istana Rama Hotel",
    "detail": "I stayed around bali in 8 hotels so far and to be honest I haven't been impressed with any of their customer service. it seems like hotels need train eir employees a little bit more and try to focus in improving their customer service skills. MY first impression at this hotel was average like any other hotel in Bali. Lobby employees were too serious and not very attentive). Had a couple more issues but the next morning I was approached by the restaurant manager to ask me about my experience at his hotel. I gave him my feedback and all the sudden I got the hotel and housekeeping managers sitting next to me. They were very interested in hearing my opinion. I was able to tell that they really care about their image and they even offer me a 50% discount to stay one more night. On top of that they offered me free drinks and food and I had a long chat (like 2 hours) with one of the managers. He took the time to give me some advice about the area, etc. I definitely recommend this hotel to anyone who is interested in being close to the ocean and next to a shopping area. This hotel is not a. 5 stars hotel, i would say is more like a 3 stars hotel. Beds were very comfortable, they provide all kind of toiletries( bar soap, gel, shampoo, shower cap, tooth brush and paste, 2 bottles of water and free coffer and tea), pool is a little outdated but water is refreshing, prices in the bar area are very affordable. I also got a free beer at check i.... I think this hotel is totally worth it...At the end of the day you get a lot for what you pay. ",
    "area": "Kuta,Bali - View on map",
